::Killfest/Scyther/Incarcinator/Slayer::

Killfest checks his scanners, seeing that Slayer was flying away much faster than he could travel by land. "I don't think I'll be able to get there in time," he replies to Kali, "But I'll send one of my troops."

He sends an order to Incarcinator, looking around the destroyed base and seeing Predacons arrive.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Scyther and Incarcinator load EndBringer and Demise into the shuttle, Incarcinator looking at the preds there. "I'm off to chase down a Trainer," he says and flies off, heading toward Slayer.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Slayer rolls, barely avoiding most of the shots, though several hit him in the back, denting his jetpack. He continues flying, though, getting further out to sea and further south.
